{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Etj jelle tahm Awim/ \nun dabbu man no turrenes diwi \ndischannus Ahſſchus/ tad fataiſi- \nfchu es tehſ tawam Tehwain/ \npar gardeem Wirrumeem/ itt \nka wiꞥſch eezeeni.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tew buhs tawam Teh. \nwam preeſcha zelt/ ka wiꞥſch \nehd/ un tew ſwehti/ pirms ka \nwiꞥſch mirſt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Jehkabs us \nRebekku fawu Mahti: Reds/ \nEesaws mans Brahlis irr weens \nſpalwainſch Wihrs/ un es eſmu \npliks.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jaſchu mans Tehws man \naptaustihs/ tad buhſchu es wiꞥ- \nna Azzis itt ka Krahpneeks/ un \nusweddiſchu pahr mann Lahstu/ \nun ne Swehtumu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazzija winna Mahte \nus winnu: lat tawi Lahſti us \nmannim paleek/ mans Dehſs: \nklaust tikſai mannai Balsi/ un \nej/ dabbu man tohs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad nogahje wiꞥſch/ un \nnehme/un atneffe fawai Mahtei/ \nun winna Mahte fataiſija gar- \ndus Wirrumus/ itt ka winna \nTehws tohs eezeenija.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Rebekka nehme Eesa- \nwa/ fawa wezzaka Dehla krahf- \nnakas Drehbes/ kas tai Naḿna \nbija/ un aptwilke tahs Jehkabam \nfawam juunakam Dehlam.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tahs Kaſlenu Ahdas \naplikke ta aptahrt winna Roh-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un winna dewe tohs \ndus Wirrumus un to Mais \nwinna bij fataiſiſſi/ Zehka \nwa Dehla Rohſa.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch nahze pee \nTehwa:un fazzija: MansTe \nun tas fazzija: tche es eſmu \neſſi tu mans Dehſs?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Jehka \nfawn Tehwu: Es eſmu E \ntaws Pirundſintajs/es eſimu \nrijs/ itt ka tu us man eſ- \nnajs/ Zellees/ luhdsams/ \ndeek/ un ehd no manna Mei \nma/ ka mann tawa Dw \nſwehti.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Jhsää \nfawu Dehlu/kas irr tas/ ka \ntik drihs eſſi atraddis/ \nDehſs? un tas fazzija: \nKUNGS taws DEews \nman to fastapt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Jhsää \nJehkabu: Mahz jelle ſthur/ \ntew aptaustu/ mans Dehle \nrig tu eſſi tas pats mans \nEesaws/ jeb ne.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Jehkabs peega \nfawa Tehwa Jhsääka/ un \naptaustija to/ un wiꞥſch f \nta Bals irr Jehkaba Bals \ntahs Rohkas irr Eesawa R\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch ne pasin \njo winna Rohkas bija sp \nnas/ itt ka winna Brahta \nwa Rohkas/ un wiꞥſch \nja to.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch fazzija:\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
